text: Greta Naemi "Ada" Onnela (23 August 1910 - 10 August 1957) was a Finnish diver. She competed in the women's 10 metre platform event at the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1910 births Category:1957 deaths Category:Finnish female divers Category:Olympic divers of Finland Category:Divers at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Vaasa
